&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Band 6 Specialist Paediatric Physiotherapist predominantly based at the Child Development Centre at City Hospital&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will work across South Nottinghamshire and Nottingham City.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful post holder will see children and young people age 0-18 years with a wide variety of neurological conditions in the centre, the child&#39;s home and schools.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A full UK driving licence and vehicle for business use is required for this post; however reasonable adjustments will be made for disabled individuals in line with the Equality Act 2010.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameAlison MiahJob titleLocality Lead PhysiotherapistEmail addressalsion.miah@nottshc.nhs.ukTelephone number07779 568945Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
